    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p1-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Business entity formation (LLC — choose state with best liability protection)\n2. Get NPI number & business insurance (malpractice + general liability)\n3. Medical Director agreement (collaborating physician — $1-3K/mo)\n4. State nursing board compliance (verify RN/NP scope of practice for IV therapy)\n5. DEA registration (if offering controlled substances like ketamine/toradol)\n6. HIPAA compliance setup (BAA with all vendors, encrypted records)\n7. Business bank account & accounting system (QuickBooks or Wave)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Business entity formation (LLC — choose state with best liability protection)\n2. Get NPI number & business insurance (malpractice + general liability)\n3. Medical Director agreement (collaborating physician — $1-3K/mo)\n4. State nursing board compliance (verify RN/NP scope of practice for IV therapy)\n5. DEA registration (if offering controlled substances like ketamine/toradol)\n6. HIPAA compliance setup (BAA with all vendors, encrypted records)\n7. Business bank account & accounting system (QuickBooks or Wave)",
