    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p2-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 448,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "1. IV therapy protocols & SOPs (Hydration, NAD+, Myers Cocktail, Immune Boost,\n   Hangover Recovery, Athletic Performance, Beauty/Glow)\n2. Supplier accounts (IV supplies, vitamins, saline, medications)\n3. Emergency protocols & adverse reaction procedures\n4. Electronic health records system (EHR — DrChrono, SimplePractice)\n5. Digital intake forms & consent waivers (JotForm, IntakeQ)\n6. Medication storage & cold chain compliance",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. IV therapy protocols & SOPs (Hydration, NAD+, Myers Cocktail, Immune Boost,\n   Hangover Recovery, Athletic Performance, Beauty/Glow)\n2. Supplier accounts (IV supplies, vitamins, saline, medications)\n3. Emergency protocols & adverse reaction procedures\n4. Electronic health records system (EHR — DrChrono, SimplePractice)\n5. Digital intake forms & consent waivers (JotForm, IntakeQ)\n6. Medication storage & cold chain compliance",
