    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p3-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 698,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "1. Service menu & pricing strategy ($150-350 per drip)\n2. Mobile unit setup (vehicle, supplies bag, portable chair, sharps disposal)\n3. Booking system (Jane App, Vagaro, or custom — online scheduling)\n4. Payment processing (Square terminal + Stripe online)\n5. Service area mapping (define radius, set travel fees by zone)\n6. Staffing plan (RNs / paramedics — 1099 vs W2 decision)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
