      "originalText": "1. Service menu & pricing strategy ($150-350 per drip)\n2. Mobile unit setup (vehicle, supplies bag, portable chair, sharps disposal)\n3. Booking system (Jane App, Vagaro, or custom — online scheduling)\n4. Payment processing (Square terminal + Stripe online)\n5. Service area mapping (define radius, set travel fees by zone)\n6. Staffing plan (RNs / paramedics — 1099 vs W2 decision)",
