    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p4-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 938,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "1. Brand identity (logo, colors, voice — luxury wellness positioning)\n2. Website (booking-optimized, SEO, testimonials, before/after gallery)\n3. Google Business Profile (critical for local SEO — \"IV therapy near me\")\n4. Social media presence (Instagram + TikTok — BTS, testimonials, education)\n5. Review generation strategy (Google, Yelp — ask after every drip)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Brand identity (logo, colors, voice — luxury wellness positioning)\n2. Website (booking-optimized, SEO, testimonials, before/after gallery)\n3. Google Business Profile (critical for local SEO — \"IV therapy near me\")\n4. Social media presence (Instagram + TikTok — BTS, testimonials, education)\n5. Review generation strategy (Google, Yelp — ask after every drip)",
