    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p5-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1158,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "1. Google Ads — local service ads (\"IV therapy near me\", \"mobile IV [city]\")\n2. Meta Ads — target wellness, fitness, nightlife, bachelorette, events\n3. Partnerships (hotels, spas, gyms, med spas, wedding planners, venues)\n4. Corporate wellness packages (office visits, team wellness days)\n5. Concierge/VIP memberships ($299-499/mo for recurring clients)\n6. Referral program (give $25, get $25 — track with unique codes)\n7. Influencer partnerships (local fitness & wellness micro-influencers)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
