    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "p6-items",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1458,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "1. Hire additional nurses (scale to 2-4 mobile teams)\n2. Multi-territory expansion (adjacent cities/suburbs)\n3. Group bookings & events (bachelorette parties, corporate, festivals)\n4. Build recurring membership base (50-100 members = $15-50K/mo recurring)\n5. Add high-ticket services (NAD+ $500-800, weight loss protocols, beauty drips)\n6. Retail add-ons (vitamin B12 shots $35-75, supplement sales)\n7. Pop-up locations (weekend wellness events, farmers markets, fitness expos)\n8. Franchise / license the model to other cities",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Hire additional nurses (scale to 2-4 mobile teams)\n2. Multi-territory expansion (adjacent cities/suburbs)\n3. Group bookings & events (bachelorette parties, corporate, festivals)\n4. Build recurring membership base (50-100 members = $15-50K/mo recurring)\n5. Add high-ticket services (NAD+ $500-800, weight loss protocols, beauty drips)\n6. Retail add-ons (vitamin B12 shots $35-75, supplement sales)\n7. Pop-up locations (weekend wellness events, farmers markets, fitness expos)\n8. Franchise / license the model to other cities",
